pique-niquer au kiosque.

359
00:21:17,778 --> 00:21:19,460
On y va, mon ours en sucre ?

360
00:21:19,710 --> 00:21:21,676
Eeyup, tarte à la crème.

361
00:21:27,566 --> 00:21:30,835
NOOON !!

